data.description: Welcome home to your gorgeous 3 bedroom/2.5 bath two-story inside the privately gated Lamplight Square.  Close proximity to Green Valley/Henderson and just north of St. Rose Parkway.  Plenty of natural light highlights your wide open kitchen with granite countertops, white cabinets, and matching appliances. First floor also features formal dining and sunken living room. Second floor features new flooring. Enjoy your large primary bedroom with dual sinks and walk-in closet.  Backyard is great for entertaining! Cool off on those hot summer days in your Community Pool. Located at the end of a cul-de-sac for your own privacy. This is truly a beautiful home!
